# Authors

CCPR is maintained by "The CCPR Authors". The copyright line in LICENSE is kept
generic on purpose, so additional contributors can be listed here without
touching per-file headers.

- Jonas Eisenhut (@jonase47) — original author and maintainer
- Oliver Trossen (@OlArtTro) — co-maintainer

To be added as a contributor, open a pull request that appends your name (and
optional handle) to this list.
